info.description:
This is really early-access. For now, only take the subversion / dev
installs. You can get it at http://svn.arlim.org/chardb_net/TgImpl/#egg=chardb-dev .

Really, it's only up here so that I can easily move it between my boxes and install it in a
virtualenv. If you want to use it, I recommend using http://svn.arlim.org/chardb_net/TgImpl/devel.py to
install it into a virtualenv.
